=Directory= 

Compiled by Nathan Schneider [http://open.therowboat.com/commons/doku.php/enterprise#platform_cooperativism]:

* [[Cooperative Networks]] - “A distributed cooperative innovation organisation” [http://networks.coop/]

* [[Fairmarket]] - “a global community of ethical producers and consumers connected by a cooperatively owned online marketplace” [http://fairmarket.coop/]

* [[Fairmondo]] - “a global, decentralised online marketplace owned by its local users” [http://www.fairmondo.com/]

* [[FairShares]] - “a brand and development model for self-governing social enterprises operating under Association, Co-operative and Company Law” [http://www.fairshares.coop/] 

* [[Mass Mosaic]], a crowd trading platform that transitioned to multi-stakeholder ownership through FairShares. [http://peoplepower.massmosaic.com/]

* [[Loconomics]] - Connecting service providers with customers. Ownership structure? [https://loconomics.com/]

“We’re readying for our launch this winter as a freelancer-owned cooperative” Said, Carolyn. “Cooperatives give new meaning to sharing economy.” SFGate. May 24, 2014.

* Member's Media [http://www.membersmedia.net/]

* Percloud - a personal cloud stack project [http://per-cloud.com/]

* Stocksy, a stock photography co-op founded in 2013. [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stocksy_United]


